### 8. **SCSS Patterns** (`form.scss`)

**Container & Layout:**
```scss
.form {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  flex: 1;
  overflow-y: auto;
  padding: $space-3;
}

.form__fields {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: $space-4;
}
```

**FormField Wrapper:**
```scss
.form-field {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: $space-1;
}

.form-field__header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: baseline;
  justify-content: space-between;
  gap: $space-2;
}

.form-field__label {
  font-size: $font-sm;
  color: $text-600;
  font-weight: $font-weight-semibold;
}

.form-field__description {
  font-size: $font-xs;
  color: $text-400;
}

.form-field__error {
  font-size: $font-xs;
  color: $color-destructive;
}
```

**Input Base Styles:**
```scss
.form-input {
  width: 100%;
  padding: $space-2 $space-3;
  background: $color-background;
  border: 1px solid $border-100;
  border-radius: $radius-md;
  color: $color-text-primary;
  font-family: $font-family;
  font-size: $font-md;
  outline: none;
  transition: border-color $transition-fast ease;

  &::placeholder {
    color: $text-400;
  }

  &:focus {
    border-color: $color-accent;
  }

  .form-field--error & {
    border-color: $color-destructive;
  }
